title: questions you’re too afraid ask your doc: sex, birth control, UTIs
itunes:title: questions you’re too afraid ask your doc: sex, birth control, UTIs
description:
Brooke and Danielle are joined by Dr. Kelly-Anne Perkins!  Dr. P shares insights on some of the gals questions that they are too afraid to ask their doc/OBGYN’s. The gals ask questions like is it bad to be on birth control for too long?  How best to prevent UTIs and infections?  The gals also discuss Dr. P’s opinion on cleaning products for down there and how often to use.
